											</LONG-NAME>
											<DESC>
												<L-2 L="EN">Reference to the linker script variants in which this group should be used.

Note:
If variants are configured but this group is not assigned to one, it applies to all of them.</L-2>
											</DESC>
											<LOWER-MULTIPLICITY>0</LOWER-MULTIPLICITY>
