						<ECUC-PARAM-CONF-CONTAINER-DEF UUID="134d1839-6bb9-45e2-b8d3-6ebf1cf56f49">
							<SHORT-NAME>vLinkGenContentTypes</SHORT-NAME>
							<DESC>
								<L-2 L="EN">This container contains all content types.

Content types can be used to automatically assign Logical Groups to an appropriate Memory Region Block depending on their expected content.


Note:
The vLinkGen comes with a predefined set of default content types. However, it is always possible to define additional ones.</L-2>
							</DESC>
